###
### SCREEN TIME LOGGING TESTS
###

### Log Screen Time
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles/screen-time
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-01-11",
  "screenTimeHours": 8.5,
  "workScreenHours": 6,
  "leisureScreenHours": 2.5,
  "deviceTypes": [
    { "device": "laptop", "hours": 6 },
    { "device": "smartphone", "hours": 2.5 }
  ],
  "appCategories": [
    { "category": "productivity", "hours": 6 },
    { "category": "social_media", "hours": 1.5 },
    { "category": "entertainment", "hours": 1 }
  ],
  "mood": "good",
  "eyeStrain": false,
  "headache": false,
  "notes": "Productive day"
}

### Get Screen Time Logs (last 7 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/screen-time?days=7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Screen Time Logs (last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/screen-time?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

